      "content": "it's just that the hotline is just people reading a script. it doesn't make the emptiness go away. it's like... if the pain is the only thing that's real right now, then isn't the only way to actually fix it to just make it stop entirely? i'm not even being dramatic, it just feels like the only logical conclusion to this much hurt.",
